title: When is the Season over?
body: I want to move up from silver 4 to gold 5 before rewards get locked in. How much time do I have?

replies.body: For NA, the ranked season ends in about 13.5 hours. There's a countdown [here](http://itsalmo.st/#theendofthe2015rankedlolseason). :]
You better go on a heavy winning streak! Good luck!
